{"abstract":[{"text":"Kind of semantic tokens which will wrap a combination of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/ColorSemanticToken","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" depending to "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"color scheme","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" (i.e. ligh mode or dark mode)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Kind of composite token with multiple values, but not named “composite” because this word is already used in the design system."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Allows to gather the multiple-value tokens from "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Figma","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" inside one object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If a color token exists with its value depending to the color scheme, it must be packed in such ``MultipleColorSemanticToken`"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleColorSemanticToken","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleColorSemanticToken\/init(_:)","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleColorSemanticToken\/init(light:dark:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleColorSemanticToken\/dark","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleColorSemanticToken\/light"],"generated":true},{"anchor":"Instance-Methods","title":"Instance Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleColorSemanticToken\/color(for:)","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleColorSemanticToken\/hasForbid